{"id":345394,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":10}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"76","ytitle":"","mtitle":"拍拉图的趣答","ftitle":"","authors":["沉雷"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一次，某人对拍拉图说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你航海多年，可曾在海上看到过什么稀罕事?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍拉图回答说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“稀罕的事是我居然安全无恙地回到陆上来了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(沉雷译)"}]}